cs.AR, cs.CV, cs.ET, cs.SY, cs.NE. 

The paper discusses the acceleration of CNNs, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of a reconfigurable logic and heterogeneous computing also falls under the categories of embedded systems (cs.ET) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper presents a hardware/software solution, which could also fit under the category of architecture (cs.AR).
